query:
DECLARE @ficha_tecnica_id INT = 31;

SELECT 
	a.title
	,CASE 
		WHEN a.[type] = 'STRING' THEN av.[value_string]
		WHEN a.[type] = 'NUMBER' THEN CONVERT(VARCHAR(50), av.[value_number])
		WHEN a.[type] = 'BOOLEAN' THEN  CONVERT(VARCHAR(50), av.[value_boolean])
		WHEN a.[type] = 'DATE' THEN  CONVERT(VARCHAR(50), av.[value_date])
		ELSE av.[value_list]
	END AS valor
	,av.record_access_key
FROM [datadriven_paranoa].[dbo].[dw_attribute_values] av
INNER JOIN dbo.dw_attribute a
	ON a.id = av.attribute_id
WHERE technical_sheet_id = @ficha_tecnica_id
AND av.is_deleted = 0
ORDER BY  av.record_access_key, title

DECLARE @ficha_tecnica_id INT = {{req.query.id_ftp}};  -- id da ficha t�cnica

SELECT * FROM
(
SELECT 
	a.attribute
	,CASE 
		WHEN a.[type] = 'STRING' THEN av.[value_string]
		WHEN a.[type] = 'NUMBER' THEN CONVERT(VARCHAR(50), av.[value_number])
		WHEN a.[type] = 'BOOLEAN' THEN  CONVERT(VARCHAR(50), av.[value_boolean])
		WHEN a.[type] = 'DATE' THEN  CONVERT(VARCHAR(50), av.[value_date])
		ELSE av.[value_list]
	END AS valor
	,av.record_access_key
FROM [datadriven_paranoa].[dbo].[dw_attribute_values] av
INNER JOIN dbo.dw_attribute a
	ON a.id = av.attribute_id
	AND a.active = 1
WHERE technical_sheet_id = @ficha_tecnica_id
	AND av.is_deleted = 0
	-- colunas do SELECT
	AND a.attribute IN ({{{queryColunasSql.coluna_select}}})
--ORDER BY  av.record_access_key, a.attribute
) tb_eav
PIVOT
-- usa a record_access_key como piv�, MIN de uma string � ela mesmo
(MIN(valor) FOR attribute IN ({{payload.coluna}})) AS PivotTable
-- coloque as colunas que deseja filtrar aqui
--WHERE codigo_produto IN ('504953950', '423910495') AND codigo_pi IN ('954385945')
WHERE {{#queryColunasSql.filtros}}
	{{^primeiro}}AND{{/primeiro}} {{filtro}} in ({{{valor}}})
{{/queryColunasSql.filtros}}
ORDER BY {{req.query.order_by}}

name: camposFichaTecnica
query:
DECLARE @technical_sheet_id INT = {{req.query.id_ftp}};

SELECT tsa.[attribute_id]
	  ,a.attribute
	  ,a.title
FROM [datadriven_paranoa].[dbo].[dw_technical_sheet_attributes] tsa
INNER JOIN dbo.dw_attribute a
	ON a.id = tsa.attribute_id
	AND a.active = 1
WHERE technical_sheet_id = @technical_sheet_id
